{"tid":1727190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比人踩到上心口，仲唔做野","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T13:53:55.000Z","uid":185713,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"70aadf0d2327cd72a82ff94cdaeb3b409d671bd7","tid":1727190,"uid":185713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:58:39.000Z","msg":"黎明行動仲做唔做可以再傾<br />\n塞唔塞返路,可以再諗<br />\n但係比老解攞彩，做哂show咁,就一定老虎蟹都唔得<br />\n我地一定要有行動回應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己淺見:<br />\n1.可以係九龍塘和理非遊行，反對老解非法干擾香港事務<br />\n原因:唔可以比佢地騎劫民意  <br />\n<br />\n2.重新係九龍塘一帶做返路障<br />\n話比共產黨聽，出老解我地唔會驚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3704cc44839eb70279f37fa65cc88ed742a12fac","tid":1727190,"uid":185713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"比啲意見"},{"pid":"6732acc88193f1ec33e644ea2589e6a4399c0f16","tid":1727190,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"係咪剩係得我一個on99,每朝等開花<br />\n<br />\n［中場檢討］係黎明行動，唔係黃昏行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725989</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"606ca39b92b54c84a4b831e01033672db16c371a","tid":1727190,"uid":252004,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bc6be145d83c387e8c1b0e8ebef9fe7330bd535","tid":1727190,"uid":185713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"606ca3